---
title: Ruby Retreat 2026
description: "Ruby Retreat is a full weekend retreat for people interested in web development to gather and be awesome together. Join us for a long weekend of hacking, learning, and socialising with fellow Rubyists at Land's Edge, Chowder Bay, right on Sydney Harbour."
url: https://retreat.ruby.org.au
image: https://retreat.ruby.org.au/images/social.jpg
---

<!-- Hero Section with Left Logo Layout -->
<section class="bg-[url('/images/cover.png')] bg-cover bg-center min-h-[22rem] text-center">
  <div class="container mx-auto mt-0 pt-16 pb-16 sm:pb-40 h-full">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8h-full">
      <!-- Left side: Logo and event details angled -->
      <div class="flex-none sm:flex">
        <img src='/images/logo.png' class='h-32 sm:h-64 block mx-auto sm:mx-0'>

        <div class="ml-6 xl:ml-12 flex-1 lg:flex-initial">
          <div class="">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-2 mt-6">
              Ruby Retreat 2026
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-emerald-800 font-semibold">
              July 3-6th, 2026
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-emerald-800">
              Land's Edge<br>
              Chowder Bay, Sydney Harbour, NSW
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right side: Blurb -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="bg-emerald-100/90 p-6 sm:rounded-lg shadow-lg mt-6 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-md">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-3">Join us for an amazing weekend</h2>
          <p class="text-emerald-800 mb-4">
            We're excited to invite you to Ruby Retreat 2026 — a long weekend of hacking, learning, and socialising
            with fellow Rubyists, right on Sydney Harbour.
          </p>
          <p class="text-emerald-800 mb-4">
            While there is a focus on Ruby, we welcome anyone
            interested in programming or web technologies to join us.
          </p>
          <p class="text-emerald-800 mb-4">
            Expect great code, great company, and a great view. We hope you can join us!
          </p>
          <a class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300" id="buy_ticket" target="_blank" href="<%= ticket_url %>">
            Get your ticket →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Pictures Section -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-emerald-900 mb-12">Retreat Highlights</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
        <%= image_tag 'slides/2.jpg', alt: 'A group of developers working outside', class: 'w-full h-64 object-cover' %>
        <div class="p-4 bg-emerald-50">
          <p class="text-emerald-800 text-center text-lg">Outdoor Coding! 👩‍💻</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
        <%= image_tag 'slides/5.jpg', alt: 'A group of people playing card games', class: 'w-full h-64 object-cover' %>
        <div class="p-4 bg-emerald-50">
          <p class="text-emerald-800 text-center text-lg">Gaming & Fun! 🕹️</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
        <%= image_tag 'slides/3.jpg', alt: 'A person swimming in a river', class: 'w-full h-64 object-cover' %>
        <div class="p-4 bg-emerald-50">
          <p class="text-emerald-800 text-center text-lg">Natural Beauty! 😍</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
        <%= image_tag 'slides/6.jpg', alt: 'A person pouring coffee into a cup', class: 'w-full h-64 object-cover' %>
        <div class="p-4 bg-emerald-50">
          <p class="text-emerald-800 text-center text-lg">Great Coffee! ☕️</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
        <%= image_tag 'slides/4.jpg', alt: 'A person smiling and giving the thumbs up', class: 'w-full h-64 object-cover' %>
        <div class="p-4 bg-emerald-50">
          <p class="text-emerald-800 text-center text-lg">Enthusiastic Encouragement! 👍</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
        <%= image_tag 'slides/1.jpg', alt: 'Two people smiling', class: 'w-full h-64 object-cover' %>
        <div class="p-4 bg-emerald-50">
          <p class="text-emerald-800 text-center text-lg">Community! 🥰</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
        <%= image_tag 'slides/7.jpg', alt: 'A person smiling', class: 'w-full h-64 object-cover' %>
        <div class="p-4 bg-emerald-50">
          <p class="text-emerald-800 text-center text-lg">Sunshine! ☀️</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
        <%= image_tag 'slides/8.jpg', alt: 'A person climbing a tree', class: 'w-full h-64 object-cover' %>
        <div class="p-4 bg-emerald-50">
          <p class="text-emerald-800 text-center text-lg">Adventure! 🌲</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Venue Section -->
<section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-100 to-green-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center text-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-6">The Venue</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-emerald-800">
          <p class="text-lg">
            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Land%27s+Edge+Harbour+Lodge,+Chowder+Bay+Rd,+Mosman+NSW+2088" class="text-emerald-800 hover:text-emerald-800 font-semibold">
              Land's Edge Harbour Lodge<br>
              Chowder Bay Rd, Mosman NSW 2088
            </a>
          </p>
          <p>
            Tucked inside Sydney Harbour National Park, the venue is right on the water. When you're ready to step
            away from the keyboard, you can bushwalk the headland trails, swim, snorkel, or kayak straight from
            the beach.
          </p>
          <p>
            We will provide more information on how to get there closer to the event.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <%= image_tag 'house.jpeg', alt: 'Warra Gnan Coastal Camp', class: 'w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg' %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Google Maps Section -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-emerald-900 mb-6">Map</h3>
      <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg mx-auto max-w-8xl bg-gray-100">
        <iframe
          src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Land%27s+Edge+Harbour+Lodge,+Chowder+Bay+Rd,+Mosman+NSW+2088&output=embed"
          width="100%"
          height="600"
          style="border:0;"
          allowfullscreen=""
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Transport Section -->
<%= partial 'parts/transport' %>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<%= partial 'parts/faq' %>

<!-- Sponsors Section -->
<%= partial 'parts/sponsors' %>

<section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-100 to-green-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Want to join us? CTA -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">Want to join us?</h3>
      <p class="text-center text-emerald-800 mb-6 text-lg">🦅 <strong>Early bird tickets</strong> are on sale now! Get in now for the best
        price!</p>

      <a class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition duration-300" href="<%= ticket_url %>" target="_blank">
        Get your ticket →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Ruby Australia Footer -->
<div class="text-center mt-16 mb-16">
  <img src="/images/rubyAU_logo_400x400.jpg" height="200" width="200" class="h-16 w-16 mx-auto mb-4" alt=""/>
  <p class="text-emerald-800">
    Ruby Retreat is a
    <a href="https://ruby.org.au/" class="text-emerald-800 hover:text-emerald-800 underline font-semibold">Ruby
      Australia</a> event, and is run under the
    <a href="https://ruby.org.au/policies/code-of-conduct" class="text-emerald-800 hover:text-emerald-800 underline font-semibold">Ruby
      Australia Code of Conduct</a>.
  </p>
  <p class="text-emerald-800 mt-2">
    For all enquiries contact
    <a class="text-emerald-800 hover:text-emerald-800 underline font-semibold" href="mailto:retreat@ruby.org.au">retreat@ruby.org.au</a>.
  </p>
</div>
